---
title: Loaded Wedges & Mexican-Spiced Chickpeas with Zesty Sour Cream & Tomato Salsa
description: Everyone loves potato wedges, that’s why we turned them into a hearty vegetarian meal. To make it work, we enlisted a few flavour-packed helping hands – chickpeas, corn, pickled onion and sour cream, plus a scattering of melted cheese. Now, it’s time to move wedges from the side to the main part of your plate!
